And I lost Darla again.

1009
00:54:43,199 --> 00:54:45,869
To Waldo. Boy, do I hate that guy.

1010
00:54:45,910 --> 00:54:48,538
Want another reason to hate him?

1011
00:54:49,205 --> 00:54:52,417
Look. The brake lever from the taxi cab.

1012
00:54:52,959 --> 00:54:55,628
The cables didn't snap, they were cut.

1013
00:54:55,712 --> 00:54:56,713
(GASPS)

1014
00:54:56,755 --> 00:55:00,133
And who would want to
see us fail more than anyone?

1015
00:55:00,300 --> 00:55:03,553
-Waldo.
-Exactly.

1016
00:55:03,595 --> 00:55:06,431
That's it. I'm gonna tear him limb from limb.

1017
00:55:06,556 --> 00:55:08,725
Boy, Waldo messed with the wrong guy.

1018
00:55:08,808 --> 00:55:10,602
And he's gonna be sorry he did.

1019
00:55:10,727 --> 00:55:13,938
'Cause I'm a caged tiger. A hurricane.

1020
00:55:14,064 --> 00:55:16,941
And when someone crosses me, they unleash

1021
00:55:17,442 --> 00:55:19,235
the sledgehammer!

1022
00:55:22,614 --> 00:55:23,656
(GASPS)

1023
00:55:24,074 --> 00:55:25,492
Did I win?

1024
00:55:27,452 --> 00:55:31,664
Alfalfa, you're a genius.
You've given me a great idea.

1025
00:55:31,748 --> 00:55:34,334
How we can raise money
and help you get Darla back.

1026
00:55:34,918 --> 00:55:37,087
Isn't that what you said last time?

1027
00:55:37,128 --> 00:55:38,963
And the time before that?

1028
00:55:39,089 --> 00:55:40,340
ALL: Yeah.

1029
00:55:40,423 --> 00:55:43,635
This time, it's a sure thing.

1030
00:55:50,934 --> 00:55:52,769
Here you are, Darla.

1031
00:55:52,852 --> 00:55:56,856
One refreshing
jumbo strawberry fizz supreme.

1032
00:55:57,315 --> 00:55:58,775
Two straws.

1033
00:55:59,192 --> 00:56:01,194
Thank you, Waldo. It's so nice of you.

1034
00:56:01,277 --> 00:56:03,822
Anything for my partner in the talent show.

1035
00:56:04,531 --> 00:56:07,283
You and I are going to be unstoppable.

1036
00:56:09,285 --> 00:56:11,871
BUCKWHEAT: Come see
the wrestling match of the century.

1037
00:56:11,955 --> 00:56:15,792
-PORKY: Tell your friends!
-Alfalfa versus the Masked Marvel.

1038
00:56:16,292 --> 00:56:18,962
Yeah, you don't want to miss it.

1039
00:56:19,004 --> 00:56:20,630
One day only.

1040
00:56:21,881 --> 00:56:25,719
Alfalfa's gonna wrestle the Masked Marvel?

1041
00:56:26,553 --> 00:56:27,846
Sounds dangerous.

1042
00:56:27,971 --> 00:56:31,057
Sounds ridiculous.
He couldn't wrestle a teddy bear.

1043
00:56:31,641 --> 00:56:35,311
I think he's pretty brave to do this.

1044
00:56:35,979 --> 00:56:38,481
Something fishy here.

1045
00:56:38,690 --> 00:56:41,026
Would you excuse me a moment, Darla?

1046
00:56:41,151 --> 00:56:43,153
Well, of course, Waldo.

1047
00:56:45,321 --> 00:56:48,074
BUCKWHEAT: Alfalfa is gonna
beat the Masked Marvel.

1048
00:56:48,158 --> 00:56:49,909
PORKY: Yeah, tell your friends.

1049
00:56:49,993 --> 00:56:51,494
Excuse me, my good man.

1050
00:56:51,703 --> 00:56:55,540
You don't happen to know
who this Masked Marvel is, do you?

1051
00:56:55,665 --> 00:56:57,542
Yeah. But it's a secret.

1052
00:56:57,667 --> 00:57:01,087
Yeah, a big secret.
Spanky told us we're not supposed to tell.

1053
00:57:01,171 --> 00:57:02,589
I don't believe it.

1054
00:57:02,672 --> 00:57:05,675
Spanky would never tell you
who the Masked Marvel is.

1055
00:57:05,759 --> 00:57:07,260
You're too little.

1056
00:57:07,344 --> 00:57:09,179
We're not too little. We know.

1057
00:57:09,262 --> 00:57:12,015
Yeah, we know exactly who it is.

1058
00:57:12,098 --> 00:57:13,391
My friend,

1059
00:57:14,351 --> 00:57:17,604
Abraham Lincoln here, says you don't.

1060
00:57:18,021 --> 00:57:21,900
I bet you $5
you don't know who the Masked Marvel is.

1061
00:57:22,192 --> 00:57:24,444
Yeah? Well, guess what.

1062
00:57:24,527 --> 00:57:26,905
I'm going to be the Masked Marvel.

1063
00:57:27,030 --> 00:57:30,617
Yeah, Porky's gonna be the Masked Marvel.
Now pay up.

1064
00:57:30,784 --> 00:57:33,411
Well, you guys sure showed me.

1065
00:57:33,870 --> 00:57:37,207
Here, don't spend it all on gum balls.

1066
00:57:42,128 --> 00:57:43,672
-Yes!
-Yeah!

1067
00:57:45,090 --> 00:57:46,174
Gentlemen.

1068
00:57:47,300 --> 00:57:49,511
Who you callin' a gentleman?

1069
00:57:49,886 --> 00:57:51,388
Whoa, whoa, whoa!

1070
00:57:51,805 --> 00:57:53,973
I'm here to make you a proposition.

1071
00:57:54,057 --> 00:57:56,851
Yeah? What kind of proposition?

1072
00:57:56,935 --> 00:57:59,229
Yeah? What kind of proposition?

1073
00:57:59,312 --> 00:58:00,897
The best kind.

1074
00:58:01,272 --> 00:58:02,982
A profitable one.

1075
00:58:03,316 --> 00:58:04,401
Give me that.

1076
00:58:05,860 --> 00:58:07,987
Oh, there's more where that came from.

1077
00:58:09,072 --> 00:58:10,740
Follow me, there's a secret entrance.

1078
00:58:10,824 --> 00:58:12,075
Hurry, I hope it hasn't started yet.

1079
00:58:12,158 --> 00:58:13,284
I don't wanna miss it.

1080
00:58:13,368 --> 00:58:15,954
-Me neither.
-WALDO: Two tickets, please.

1081
00:58:16,037 --> 00:58:17,956
DARLA: Thanks for inviting me, Waldo.

1082
00:58:18,039 --> 00:58:20,542
Normally, I abhor violence,

1083
00:58:20,750 --> 00:58:23,294
but this seemed too good to miss.

1084
00:58:23,670 --> 00:58:26,006
Enjoy the match. Next!

1085
00:58:28,800 --> 00:58:30,844
Popcorn! Get your popcorn!

1086
00:58:30,927 --> 00:58:35,306
Can't enjoy a wrestling match
without a big old bag of popcorn.

1087
00:58:36,516 --> 00:58:37,892
Thank you.

1088
00:58:40,770 --> 00:58:42,772
Popcorn! Get your popcorn!

1089
00:58:42,939 --> 00:58:44,357
Welcome to the match.

1090
00:58:45,608 --> 00:58:46,693
Welcome.

1091
00:58:47,652 --> 00:58:49,779
Psst. Spank. How we doing so far?

1092
00:58:49,863 --> 00:58:51,573
Great. We got a full house.

1093
00:58:51,656 --> 00:58:53,450
Boy, are we gonna clean up.

1094
00:58:56,578 --> 00:58:58,621
-I'll take that.
-(WORM LAUGHS)

1095
00:58:59,080 --> 00:59:01,166
KID: I paid good money for that.

1096
00:59:06,421 --> 00:59:10,967
I just hope Alfalfa doesn't
hurt the Masked Marvel too badly.

1097
00:59:11,051 --> 00:59:14,304
Oh, I wouldn't worry about that.

1098
00:59:23,855 --> 00:59:27,400
(GASPS) Hey, this area is for wrestlers only.

1099
00:59:27,650 --> 00:59:30,612
-There's been a change of plan.
-Yeah.

1100
00:59:31,154 --> 00:59:32,197
(YELPS)

1101
00:59:33,782 --> 00:59:35,367
Hello, Spanky.

1102
00:59:35,867 --> 00:59:39,245
Waldo? I didn't think of you
as the wrestling type.

1103
00:59:40,413 --> 00:59:42,624
I couldn't pass up the opportunity

1104
00:59:42,707 --> 00:59:46,127
to see the Masked Marvel
wipe the floor with Alfalfa.

1105
00:59:46,211 --> 00:59:48,588
Oh, yeah?
You're gonna be disappointed, Waldo.

1106
00:59:48,672 --> 00:59:51,132
There's no way Alfalfa's going to lose.

1107
00:59:51,216 --> 00:59:53,843
Oh, really? Care to make it interesting?

1108
00:59:54,135 --> 00:59:55,762
What do you mean?

1109
00:59:56,346 --> 00:59:59,849
I'll bet you all the money
you've made from collecting admissions

1110
00:59:59,933 --> 01:00:03,061
that Alfalfa is going to lose.

1111
01:00:04,938 --> 01:00:07,190
You're on, Waldo. It's a bet.

1112
01:00:07,232 --> 01:00:08,400
(SPITS)

1113
01:00:18,201 --> 01:00:19,744
Sucker.

1114
01:00:23,957 --> 01:00:25,583
Showtime, Porky.

1115
01:00:25,667 --> 01:00:28,628
Wow, Porky. The costume looks great on you.

1116
01:00:30,130 --> 01:00:31,715
You even look taller.

1117
01:00:32,632 --> 01:00:35,218
Oh, and remember,
when I give you the high sign,

1118
01:00:35,343 --> 01:00:36,970
that's your cue to take a dive. Got it?

1119
01:00:39,889 --> 01:00:41,307
(BOTH SIGH)

1120
01:00:47,856 --> 01:00:50,734
Ladies and gentlemen.

1121
01:00:50,817 --> 01:00:55,238
Welcome to the world
championship wrestling match of all time.

1122
01:00:55,363 --> 01:00:56,406
(CROWD CHEERING)

1123
01:01:01,745 --> 01:01:02,829
(BARKS)

1124
01:01:03,997 --> 01:01:07,250
Are you ready to wrestle?

1125
01:01:07,417 --> 01:01:08,835
(CHEERING)

1126
01:01:10,837 --> 01:01:15,675
In this corner,
the most dangerous man in wrestling.

1127
01:01:15,925 --> 01:01:21,264
Let's hear it
for the undefeated "Wildcat" Alfalfa.

1128
01:01:21,723 --> 01:01:22,766
(CHEERING)

1129
01:01:26,227 --> 01:01:28,772
CROWD: Alfalfa! Alfalfa!

1130
01:01:29,272 --> 01:01:32,901
How is he undefeated
if he's never wrestled before?

1131
01:01:32,942 --> 01:01:35,028
That's why he's undefeated.

1132
01:01:35,695 --> 01:01:36,780
Ah...

1133
01:01:36,905 --> 01:01:39,449
In this corner, his opponent,

1134
01:01:39,574 --> 01:01:42,452
the most feared man in wrestling.

1135
01:01:42,577 --> 01:01:45,538
The man, the myth, the legend,

1136
01:01:45,622 --> 01:01:48,708
the Masked Marvel!

1137
01:01:49,042 --> 01:01:50,543
(CROWD BOOING)

1138
01:01:51,461 --> 01:01:53,713
Whoo! Go, Masked Marvel!

1139
01:01:53,963 --> 01:01:55,423
-(CHEERING)
-(BOOING)

1140
01:01:57,425 --> 01:01:59,886
Okay, men, bring it in. Shake hands.

1141
01:01:59,969 --> 01:02:02,263
Men, I wanna see a fair fight.

1142
01:02:02,889 --> 01:02:05,141
Good luck and may the best man win.

1143
01:02:05,266 --> 01:02:07,143
And remember, Porky, make it look real.

1144
01:02:08,812 --> 01:02:10,313
(CHEERING)

1145
01:02:13,983 --> 01:02:15,610
And, fight.

1146
01:02:16,653 --> 01:02:17,987
CROWD: (CHANTING) Yeah! Alfalfa!

1147
01:02:18,071 --> 01:02:19,614
Ooh, yeah!

1148
01:02:20,156 --> 01:02:21,324
(CHANTING)

1149
01:02:23,827 --> 01:02:24,828
(YELLING)

1150
01:02:27,997 --> 01:02:29,165
Oh.

1151
01:02:30,500 --> 01:02:31,960
-Ooh. (LAUGHS)
-(GROANS)

1152
01:02:34,004 --> 01:02:35,630
Are you okay?

1153
01:02:35,672 --> 01:02:37,257
He knows he's supposed to lose, right?

1154
01:02:37,507 --> 01:02:39,509
Yeah. He's just makin' it look good.

1155
01:02:39,592 --> 01:02:41,261
Now get back in there, champ.

1156
01:02:41,845 --> 01:02:43,847
CROWD: Go, Alfalfa!

1157
01:02:46,307 --> 01:02:48,018
Go, Masked Marvel.

1158
01:02:48,184 --> 01:02:49,686
Okay, Masked Marvel.

1159
01:02:49,811 --> 01:02:53,106
Get ready for my
signature move, the pulverizer.

1160
01:02:53,189 --> 01:02:55,525
It puts the "ow" in pow!

1161
01:02:59,487 --> 01:03:00,780
(CROWD GASPING)

1162
01:03:01,364 --> 01:03:02,449
(BELL RINGS)

1163
01:03:02,699 --> 01:03:05,702
CROWD: Alfalfa! Alfalfa!

1164
01:03:13,543 --> 01:03:16,546
Alfalfa! Alfalfa!

1165
01:03:17,005 --> 01:03:18,465
(MUFFLED GRUNTING)

1166
01:03:21,885 --> 01:03:23,053
(POUNDING)

1167
01:03:28,683 --> 01:03:31,561
Holy guacamole. What happened?

1168
01:03:31,603 --> 01:03:33,355
(MUFFLED CRIES)

1169
01:03:35,732 --> 01:03:36,733
Hmm?

1170
01:03:37,359 --> 01:03:38,735
(CROWD CHEERING)

1171
01:03:40,070 --> 01:03:41,112
(WHINES)

1172
01:03:41,613 --> 01:03:42,739
And, fight.

1173
01:03:43,198 --> 01:03:45,575
CROWD: (CHANTING) Alfalfa! Alfalfa!

1174
01:03:47,077 --> 01:03:48,536
(YELLING)

1175
01:03:51,414 --> 01:03:52,707
Yes!

1176
01:03:54,250 --> 01:03:55,377
Whoa!

1177
01:03:58,630 --> 01:03:59,923
Porky.

1178
01:04:00,757 --> 01:04:02,967
Don't you see he's giving you the high sign?

1179
01:04:03,093 --> 01:04:05,428
-Oh, I can't watch!
-I can.

1180
01:04:06,429 --> 01:04:07,931
You're supposed to make it look real.

1181
01:04:09,891 --> 01:04:11,101
Not that real!

1182
01:04:13,269 --> 01:04:15,772
I don't remember this as part of the plan.

1183
01:04:15,897 --> 01:04:17,273
Me neither.

1184
01:04:19,484 --> 01:04:20,485
Spanky!

1185
01:04:20,568 --> 01:04:22,487
-Spanky! Spanky!
-(GASPS)

1186
01:04:24,114 --> 01:04:25,990
-Psst.
-(GROANS)

1187
01:04:26,950 --> 01:04:28,118
(SOFTLY) Alfalfa.

1188
01:04:29,744 --> 01:04:30,787
(GASPS)

1189
01:04:31,621 --> 01:04:34,124
If Porky's there, then who's...

1190
01:04:36,793 --> 01:04:37,836
(GASPS)

1191
01:04:38,294 --> 01:04:39,462
Butch.

1192
01:04:40,672 --> 01:04:42,632
-Butch!
-(GASPS)

1193
01:04:44,968 --> 01:04:46,177
(GROWLS)

1194
01:04:46,845 --> 01:04:47,971
(GIGGLES NERVOUSLY)

1195
01:04:48,013 --> 01:04:51,141
Run, Alfalfa, run! Run for your life!

1196
01:05:04,279 --> 01:05:05,822
-(GROANS)
-Ooh!

1197
01:05:06,656 --> 01:05:08,450
What are you doing?

1198
01:05:09,284 --> 01:05:10,493
(SCREAMING)

1199
01:05:18,793 --> 01:05:19,836
Ooh!

1200
01:05:20,545 --> 01:05:21,671
Oh, no.

1201
01:05:25,133 --> 01:05:27,886
Yeah! And the winner is Butch!

1202
01:05:28,887 --> 01:05:29,971
(GROANS)

1203
01:05:32,891 --> 01:05:36,353
This isn't fair.
You cheated by putting Butch in the match.

1204
01:05:37,562 --> 01:05:40,690
And you cheated
by rigging the match with Porky.

1205
01:05:40,732 --> 01:05:42,525
I just cheated better.

1206
01:05:42,650 --> 01:05:45,028
But don't worry, it's going to a good cause.

1207
01:05:45,362 --> 01:05:48,990
I'm going to use the money
to put a security system in the tree house,

1208
01:05:49,532 --> 01:05:52,035
so I can keep you all out for good.

1209
01:05:52,494 --> 01:05:53,995
Come on, Darla.

1210
01:05:56,247 --> 01:05:57,874
DARLA: Sorry, Alfalfa.

1211
01:05:58,541 --> 01:06:01,503
You lost all our money, Spank?

1212
01:06:01,670 --> 01:06:04,422
How come you didn't ask us
before you did that?

1213
01:06:04,547 --> 01:06:05,882
BOTH: Yeah!

1214
01:06:06,049 --> 01:06:08,218
Because I'm the leader and I had to make

1215
01:06:08,343 --> 01:06:10,679
a split-second, executive decision.

1216
01:06:10,720 --> 01:06:12,555
I almost got killed for nothing.

1217
01:06:12,681 --> 01:06:15,183
Okay, so I made a bad call.

1218
01:06:15,225 --> 01:06:17,310
But don't worry. I'll come up with one

1219
01:06:17,394 --> 01:06:19,437
of my great ideas any second now.

1220
01:06:19,562 --> 01:06:21,940
Every time you come
up with one of your great ideas,

1221
01:06:22,065 --> 01:06:23,400
something bad happens.

1222
01:06:23,441 --> 01:06:24,567
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

1223
01:06:24,609 --> 01:06:27,153
Well, someone has
to do the thinking around here.

1224
01:06:27,404 --> 01:06:31,408
You guys would be helpless without me.
Right, Alfalfa?

1225
01:06:33,660 --> 01:06:34,911
Alfalfa?

1226
01:06:35,120 --> 01:06:36,454
They're right, Spank.

1227
01:06:36,579 --> 01:06:40,166
We're all supposed to act as a team,
but you never act that way.

1228
01:06:40,250 --> 01:06:41,292
Ever.

1229
01:06:41,418 --> 01:06:44,754
And now, thanks to you,
it's too late to save Grandma's bakery.

1230
01:06:44,838 --> 01:06:47,507
It's over. We lost. Come on, guys.

1231
01:06:48,842 --> 01:06:51,094
Hey. Where are you going? Come back.

1232
01:06:51,302 --> 01:06:53,179
We still have a little time left.

1233
01:06:53,930 --> 01:06:55,932
Porky? Buckwheat?

1234
01:06:56,474 --> 01:06:59,269
You're too bossy, Spanky.

1235
01:06:59,310 --> 01:07:01,146
Yeah, too bossy.

1236
01:07:02,272 --> 01:07:03,440
(SIGHS)

1237
01:07:03,523 --> 01:07:04,607
Petey?

1238
01:07:05,358 --> 01:07:06,609
(WHINES)

1239
01:07:14,284 --> 01:07:15,535
(SIGHS)

1240
01:07:51,488 --> 01:07:53,198
Oh, Spanky!

1241
01:07:53,865 --> 01:07:55,241
(LAUGHS)

1242
01:07:55,408 --> 01:07:58,036
Want a muffin? It's hot.

1243
01:07:58,161 --> 01:08:01,331
No, thanks, Grandma. I'm not really hungry.

1244
01:08:02,165 --> 01:08:04,167
A Rascal doesn't want a muffin?

1245
01:08:04,250 --> 01:08:06,544
I've never heard of that before.

1246
01:08:08,672 --> 01:08:10,840
Never get tired of this.

1247
01:08:11,508 --> 01:08:12,676
Oh...

1248
01:08:13,718 --> 01:08:16,513
I'm gonna miss this old bakery.

1249
01:08:17,681 --> 01:08:19,683
I'm really sorry, Grandma.

1250
01:08:19,766 --> 01:08:22,852
Been trying so hard to make money to save it.

1251
01:08:23,228 --> 01:08:28,525
Spanky, I do appreciate
all of you trying to help me, honey.

1252
01:08:29,442 --> 01:08:31,736
But you're losing your bakery.

1253
01:08:32,278 --> 01:08:34,614
And we're losing our tree house.

1254
01:08:34,698 --> 01:08:38,284
You have your friends.
That's what's important.

1255
01:08:38,368 --> 01:08:41,454
Not anymore. They're all mad at me.

1256
01:08:41,579 --> 01:08:43,248
They say I'm bossy.

1257
01:08:43,373 --> 01:08:45,417
Well, is that true?

1258
01:08:45,542 --> 01:08:49,129
I'm not bossy. I just tell people what to do.

1259
01:08:49,546 --> 01:08:52,382
(CHUCKLES) That sounds kind
of bossy to me.

1260
01:08:53,216 --> 01:08:55,719
